name: JavaScript
description: A high-level, interpreted programming language that is widely used for web development, both client-side and server-side applications. JavaScript is a dynamic, weakly typed language that supports multiple programming paradigms including object-oriented, imperative, and functional programming styles. It's the foundation of modern web development and powers interactive websites, web applications, mobile apps, desktop applications, and server-side services.
